               <p>SEVENTH DAY, THURSDAY, SEPTEMBER 23. OLD COURT.</p>
               <p>Middlesex Cases, First Jury, Before Mr. Sergeant 
               <persName id="t18240916-258-person2158">Arabin</persName>
            .</p>

               <p>1407. 
               
                  <persName id="t18240916-258-defend2160" type="defendantName">
                     WILLIAM 
                     TAYLOR
                  <interp inst="t18240916-258-defend2160" type="surname" value="TAYLOR"></interp>
